    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to finance.gl_account. Business justification: Each invoice line posts to a specific GL account for product revenue; linking enables line-level GL reporting required for statutory and internal financial statements.' ;
    rdfs:domain ind:ChemicalMfg ;
